data_table.description: Endothelial Progenitor Cell Lab Assay, Offspring Exam 8 and Omni 1 Exam 3. EPC number and proliferative function were assessed on specimens obtained from Framingham Offspring Study participants attending the 8th quadrennial examination. Number was assessed using flow cytometry to define the following cell populations: CD34+, AC133+, CD34+/KDR+, CD31+/CD45+. Proliferative function was assayed with a standard EPC colony forming unit assay. l_epc_2007_m_0041s replaces epc1_2007s.
